#: templates/info/install.html:10
msgid "Python 3.5+ is a requirement."
msgstr "Python 3.5+ ni sharti."

#: templates/info/install.html:13
msgid ""
"Download project from <a href=\"https://github.com/jact/openclinic-in-django/"
"\">GitHub</a> and decompress file."
msgstr "Pakua maradi kutoka <a href=\"https://github.com/jact/openclinic-in-django/\">GitHub</a> na ufungue faili."

#: templates/info/install.html:17
msgid "Execute these commands in a terminal from project directory:"
msgstr "Tekeleza amri hizi kwenye terminal kutoka kwa saraka ya mradi:"

#: templates/info/install.html:29
msgid ""
"Access your new <a href=\"/\">clinic system</a>. Enter <code><kbd>admin</"
"kbd></code> for both, the login and password whenever you are prompted to "
"sign on."
msgstr "Fikia <a href=\"/\">mfumo wako mpya wa kliniki</a>. Ingiza <code><kbd>admin</kbd></code> kwa jina la mtumiaji na nenosiri wakati wowote unapoombwa kuingia."

#: templates/info/install.html:33
msgid "It's advisable to change the admin user's password."
msgstr "Inashauriwa kubadilisha nenosiri la mtumiaji wa wasimamizi."

#: templates/info/readme.html:9
msgid "Welcome to OpenClinic!"
msgstr "Karibu OpenClinic!"

#: templates/info/readme.html:11
msgid ""
"First of all, thanks a lot to download this software, I hope that you can "
"enjoy it."
msgstr "Kwanza kabisa, asante sana kwa kupakua programu hii, natumai utaifurahia."

#: templates/info/readme.html:13
msgid ""
"OpenClinic is free software, released under GNU GPL Licence version 3.0 (see "
"<a href=\"/info/license\">LICENSE</a> file for details)."
msgstr "OpenClinic ni programu huria, iliyotolewa chini ya GNU GPL Leseni toleo la 3.0 (ona faili ya <a href=\"/info/license\">LICENSE</a> kwa maelezo)."

#: templates/info/readme.html:15 templates/info/readme.html:127
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Utangulizi"

#: templates/info/readme.html:17
msgid ""
"OpenClinic is an easy to use, open source, medical records system written in "
"Django."
msgstr "OpenClinic ni mfumo wa rekodi za matibabu wa chanzo huria na rahisi kutumia ulioandikwa kwa Django."

#: templates/info/readme.html:17
msgid ""
"It has been mainly thougth for private clinics, surgeries and private "
"doctors."
msgstr "Imefikiriwa zaidi kwa kliniki za kibinafsi, upasuaji na madaktari wa kibinafsi."

#: templates/info/readme.html:17
msgid "It is platform independent and it has multilanguage architecture."
msgstr "Haidhaminiwi na jukwaa lolote na ina usanifu wa lugha nyingi."

#: templates/info/readme.html:19
msgid "Currently OpenClinic has the following sections:"
msgstr "Kwa sasa OpenClinic ina sehemu zifuatazo:"

#: templates/info/readme.html:23 templates/info/welcome.html:25
msgid "Use this section to manage your patient's medical records."
msgstr "Tumia sehemu hii kudhibiti rekodi za matibabu za wagonjwa wako."

#: templates/info/readme.html:25 templates/info/welcome.html:27
msgid "Patient's Administration:"
msgstr "Usimamizi wa Wagonjwa:"

#: templates/info/readme.html:28 templates/info/welcome.html:30
msgid "Search, new, delete, edit"
msgstr "Tafuta, mpya, futa, hariri"

#: templates/info/readme.html:30
msgid "Social Data"
msgstr "Data ya Kijamii"

#: templates/info/readme.html:32 templates/info/welcome.html:32
msgid "Clinic History"
msgstr "Historia ya Kliniki"

#: templates/info/readme.html:34 templates/info/welcome.html:33
msgid "Problem Reports"
msgstr "Ripoti za Matatizo"

#: templates/info/readme.html:39 templates/info/welcome.html:48
msgid "Use this section to manage administrative settings."
msgstr "Tumia sehemu hii kudhibiti mipangilio ya utawala."

#: templates/info/readme.html:42 templates/info/welcome.html:51
msgid "Staff members"
msgstr "Wafanyakazi"

#: templates/info/readme.html:44
msgid "System Users"
msgstr "Watumiaji wa Mfumo"

#: templates/info/readme.html:49 templates/info/readme.html:129
msgid "Requirements"
msgstr "Mahitaji"

#: templates/info/readme.html:61
msgid "a web server prepared to execute Django code"
msgstr "seva ya wavuti iliyoandaliwa kutekeleza nambari ya Django"

#: templates/info/readme.html:65
msgid "and, of course, a web browser (with enabled JavaScript)"
msgstr "na, bila shaka, kivinjari cha wavuti (kilicho na JavaScript inayoweza kutumika)"

#: templates/info/readme.html:69
msgid ""
"For more details, see <a href=\"/info/install\">Install instructions</a>."
msgstr "Kwa maelezo zaidi, ona <a href=\"/info/install\">Maelekezo ya Usakinishaji</a>."

#: templates/info/readme.html:71 templates/info/readme.html:131
msgid "Features"
msgstr "Sifa"

#: templates/info/readme.html:74
msgid "Environment: Web Environment"
msgstr "Mazingira: Mazingira ya Wavuti"

#: templates/info/readme.html:76
msgid "Intended Audience: Education, Healthcare industry"
msgstr "Hadhira Inayolengwa: Elimu, Sekta ya afya"

#: templates/info/readme.html:80
msgid "Natural Language: English, Spanish"
msgstr "Lugha ya Asili: Kiingereza, Kihispania"

#: templates/info/readme.html:82
msgid "Operating System: OS Independent"
msgstr "Mfumo wa Uendeshaji: Haukubaliani na OS yoyote"

#: templates/info/readme.html:84
msgid "Programming Language: Python"
msgstr "Lugha ya Programu: Python"

#: templates/info/readme.html:86
msgid "Topic: Dynamic Content"
msgstr "Mada: Maudhui Yenye Nguvu"

#: templates/info/readme.html:89 templates/info/readme.html:133
msgid "Multilingual Support"
msgstr "Usaidizi wa Lugha Nyingi"

#: templates/info/readme.html:91
msgid ""
"OpenClinic offers multilingual support, so anyone who wants to contribute a "
"language can create a new .po file (portable object) and enjoy his/her own "
"language. Every language that it send to me will be included in the next "
"release."
msgstr "OpenClinic inatoa usaidizi wa lugha nyingi, kwa hivyo yeyote anayetaka kuchangia lugha anaweza kuunda faili mpya ya .po (portable object) na kufurahia lugha yake mwenyewe. Kila lugha inayotumwa kwangu itajumuishwa katika toleo linalofuata."

#: templates/info/readme.html:93 templates/info/readme.html:135
msgid "Download"
msgstr "Pakua"

#: templates/info/readme.html:95
msgid ""
"You can get the newest version at <a href=\"https://github.com/jact/"
"openclinic-in-django\">GitHub</a>."
msgstr "Unaweza kupata toleo jipya zaidi kwenye <a href=\"https://github.com/jact/openclinic-in-django\">GitHub</a>."

#: templates/info/readme.html:97 templates/info/readme.html:137
msgid "Developers Information"
msgstr "Maelezo ya Watayarishaji"

#: templates/info/readme.html:102
msgid "principal developer of OpenClinic project"
msgstr "mtayarishaji mkuu wa mradi wa OpenClinic"

#: templates/info/readme.html:104
msgid "person in charge of OpenClinic's maintenance service since autumn 2002"
msgstr "mtu anayehusika na huduma ya matengenezo ya OpenClinic tangu vuli ya 2002"

#: templates/info/readme.html:106 templates/info/readme.html:112
msgid "person in charge of the project"
msgstr "mtu anayehusika na mradi"

#: templates/info/readme.html:115 templates/info/readme.html:139
msgid "Farewell"
msgstr "Kwaheri"

#: templates/info/readme.html:117
msgid ""
"Please, enjoy OpenClinic and remember that this is <a href=\"http://"
"www.gnu.org/licenses/old-licenses/gpl-3.0.en.html\">free GPL software</a>."
msgstr "Tafadhali, furahia OpenClinic na ukumbuke kuwa hii ni <a href=\"http://www.gnu.org/licenses/old-licenses/gpl-3.0.en.html\">programu huria ya GPL</a>."

#: templates/info/readme.html:119
msgid ""
"OpenClinic isn't perfect, but your <a href=\"https://github.com/jact/"
"openclinic-in-django/issues\">suggestions, feedback and bug reports</a> can "
"help us to have a very well done medical records system!"
msgstr "OpenClinic sio kamili, lakini <a href=\"https://github.com/jact/openclinic-in-django/issues\">mapendekezo yako, maoni na ripoti za hitilafu</a> zinaweza kutusaidia kuwa na mfumo wa rekodi za matibabu uliofanywa vizuri sana!"

